spired by Chabon’s grandfather’s deathbed confessions while he’s on painkillers. From pre-war South Philly to Germany to a Florida retirement home, to a prison in New York, the novel collapses one man’s life into a week. As Goodreads puts it, it’s “","position":{"start":{"line":88,"column":218,"offset":11135},"end":{"line":88,"column":474,"offset":11391}}},{"type":"raw","value":"<span id=\"freeText3345685399332595511\">","position":{"start":{"line":88,"column":474,"offset":11391},"end":{"line":88,"column":513,"offset":11430}}},{"type":"text","value":"a work of fictional non-fiction, an autobiography wrapped in a novel disguised as a memoir, ","position":{"start":{"line":88,"column":513,"offset":11430},"end":{"line":88,"column":605,"offset":11522}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Moonglow","position":{"start":{"line":88,"column":606,"offset":11523},"end":{"line":88,"column":614,"offset":11531}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":88,"column":605,"offset":11522},"end":{"line":88,"column":615,"offset":11532}}},{"type":"text","value":" is Chabon at his most daring, his most moving, his most Chabonesque.” While I enjoyed it, and this problem may be mine, but I had a hard time following the story in some spots.","position":{"start":{"line":88,"column":615,"offset":11532},"end":{"line":88,"column":792,"offset":11709}}},{"type":"raw","value":"</span>","position":{"start":{"line":88,"column":792,"offset":11709},"end":{"line":88,"column":799,"offset":11716}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":88,"column":1,"offset":10918},"end":{"line":88,"column":799,"offset":11716}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4643/38730926394_31cb214012.jpg","alt":null},"children":[],"position":{"start":{"line":90,"column":1,"offset":11718},"end":{"line":90,"column":68,"offset":11785}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":90,"column":1,"offset":11718},"end":{"line":90,"column":68,"offset":11785}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"15. In the Shadows of the American Century by Alfred McCoy","position":{"start":{"line":92,"column":3,"offset":11789},"end":{"line":92,"column":61,"offset":11847}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":92,"column":1,"offset":11787},"end":{"line":92,"column":63,"offset":11849}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":92,"column":1,"offset":11787},"end":{"line":92,"column":63,"offset":11849}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I find myself asking why did I choose to end the year reading this particular book? I read an excerpt from the author on Brain Pickings and was inspired to order it from Amazon. Ending the year with a downer book isn’t necessarily a bad thing: sure, I’ve got different scenarios for the end of the world playing through my head, but the scariest part is that all of these are not too far from reality. Maybe it’ll somehow make me more optimistic in 2018, but I’m almost afraid to ask myself ‘how much worse could things get?’ The end of the book really forces you to put on your tin foil hat while McCoy takes you through five possible scenarios for the demise of the empire of the United States of America. As we all know by now, Trump is not the cause of the downfall, he is merely a symptom of it. By 2030/2040 it looks like China will surely be on top and it’s largely unclear what the role of the States will be.","position":{"start":{"line":94,"column":1,"offset":11851},"end":{"line":94,"column":918,"offset":12768}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":94,"column":1,"offset":11851},"end":{"line":94,"column":918,"offset":12768}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I still remain hopeful for 2018. Happy New Year y’all!","position":{"start":{"line":96,"column":1,"offset":12770},"end":{"line":96,"column":55,"offset":12824}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":96,"column":1,"offset":12770},"end":{"line":96,"column":55,"offset":12824}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":96,"column":55,"offset":12824}}}}